<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٧٣:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: {كَلَّا إِنَّ الْإِنْسَانَ لَيَطْغَى <span class="c2">(٦)</span> أَنْ رَآهُ اسْتَغْنَى <span class="c2">(٧)</span> إِنَّ إِلَى رَبِّكَ الرُّجْعَى <span class="c2">(٨)</span>} <span class="c4">[العلق: ٦ - ٨]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ مَعْمَرٌ:</span> <span class="c3">{الرُّجْعَى}</span>: <span class="c2">«المَرْجِعُ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>